{"id":1322,"date":"2024-08-04T19:45:10","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T19:45:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1322"},"modified":"2024-08-04T19:45:10","modified_gmt":"2024-08-04T19:45:10","slug":"mission-006","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-006\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #006: All the Right Moves"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Mission #006: All the Right Moves<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Polder Town, house near Safari Zone entrance &#8211; woman near TV<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Completed main story missions up until Polder Town<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Collect all 120 TMs in Borrius<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>Gold Bottle Cap<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>A woman in Polder Town gives you a huge task &#8211; find all of the 120 TMs in Borrius, and she\u2019ll give you a valuable Gold Bottle Cap.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/006\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-house-near-the-safari-zone-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"The house near the Safari Zone entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The house near the Safari Zone entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once you make it to Polder Town in West Borrius, walk to the east side of town and you\u2019ll see the entrance to the Safari Zone. <\/p>\n<p>Just above that is a house (pictured in the screenshot above).<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/006\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-huge-collecting-task-begins.jpg\" alt=\"The huge collecting task begins \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The huge collecting task begins<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Speak to the woman near the TV and she\u2019ll give you a very long yet important collection mission &#8211; track down and acquire all 120 TMs in the Borrius Region.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/006\/03-pokemon-unbound-a-tm-found-in-the-wild.jpg\" alt=\"A TM found in the wild \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>A TM found in the wild<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>TMs can be found in a lot of places, though the vast majority of them are found in the wild as yellow Poke Balls.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/006\/04-pokemon-unbound-a-tm-earned-through-battle.jpg\" alt=\"A TM earned through battle \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>A TM earned through battle<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>They can also be given to you by NPCs just by talking to them, as mission rewards, or as rewards for defeating them &#8211; all of the Gym Leaders give you one, for example.<\/p>\n<p>For detailed information on how to find them you can refer to <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\">our TM &#038; HM page<\/a> listing all of their locations.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/006\/05-pokemon-unbound-using-the-gold-bottle-cap.jpg\" alt=\"Using the Gold Bottle Cap \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using the Gold Bottle Cap<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Your reward for finding all 120 TMs is a Gold Bottle Cap, an incredibly rare and useful item.<\/p>\n<p>Bottle Caps will max out one stat\u2019s IV, while Gold Bottle Caps will max out all stats\u2019 IVs.<\/p>\n<div class=\"callout-box\">There\u2019s a woman in Seaport City, just south of the eastern warehouse, who will accept Bottle Caps and Gold Bottle Caps in exchange for increasing the IVs &#8211; the Individual Values (stat growth potential) &#8211; of a single Pok\u00e9mon.<\/div>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1323,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1322","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1322","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1323"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1322"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1322"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":tr